Facebook Login now sees uses in 81 percent of iOS apps and 62 percent of Android apps. And with more than a billion users, Facebook itself is winning the identity war.
All that adds up to an awful lot of new account signups through Facebook Login.
As Facebook shared with us today, people download more than 850 million apps each month with signups occurring through Facebook Login.
